<!-- [DocumentBodyStart:d568ce95-c2c9-445f-95a6-937630d1bb4b] --><div class="jive-rendered-content"><p><strong>Scope</strong></p><p>All customers using Red Hat Decision Manager 7.0.0</p><p style="min-height: 8pt; padding: 0px;">&#160;</p><p><strong>Severity</strong></p><p>Informational</p><p style="min-height: 8pt; padding: 0px;">&#160;</p><p><strong>Description</strong></p><p>We are pleased to announce that Red Hat Decision Manager (RHDM) 7.0.1 is now available. This is a follow-up patch for version 7.0.0 which brings increased stability.</p><p style="min-height: 8pt; padding: 0px;">&#160;</p><div><div>RHDM patch releases for 7.x include full distributions of all components that enables customers to get started with the latest patches without having to start at an earlier major/minor release and then apply patches.</div><div> </div><div>This release also includes:</div><ul><li>A patch distribution [1] that enables customers to patch existing deployments of RHDM is also available with the release</li><li>OpenShift templates [2] that lets you get started with RHDM on OpenShift and also sources for container images for customers looking to build their own custom images</li><li>Localization in the UI (Decision Central) for the Japanese language.</li></ul><p style="min-height: 8pt; padding: 0px;">&#160;</p><p><strong>LINKS</strong></p><ol><li>Patch distribution: <a class="jive-link-external-small" href="https://mojo.redhat.com/external-link.jspa?url=https%3A%2F%2Faccess.redhat.com%2Fjbossnetwork%2Frestricted%2FsoftwareDetail.html%3FsoftwareId%3D59321%26product%3Drhdm%26version%3D7.0.1%26downloadType%3Ddistributions" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://access.redhat.com/jbossnetwork/restricted/softwareDetail.html?softwareId=59321&amp;product=rhdm&amp;version=7.0.1&amp;downloadType=distributions</a>&#160;</li><li>OpenShift templates: <a class="jive-link-external-small" href="https://mojo.redhat.com/external-link.jspa?url=https%3A%2F%2Faccess.redhat.com%2Fjbossnetwork%2